languages.text: "Эти джунгли... скрывают хищников опаснее тех, что страшат когтями и клыками. Я слышу... среди них есть вожак. Ближе, чем вы думаете..."
"There are worse beasts lurking in this jungle, and they don't have claws and fangs. I can hear... they have a leader among them. And he is closer than you think..."

languages.text: “这片丛林里潜伏着更加可怕的野兽，而且它们并没有爪子与獠牙。我能听到……它们之中有一位领袖，而且他与你的距离，比你想象得还要更近……”

languages.text: «Hay peores bestias acechando en esta jungla, y no tienen garras ni colmillos. Puedo oírlas... tienen un líder. Y está más cerca de lo que creemos...».

languages.text: 「このジャングルにはもっと恐ろしい獣が潜んでいるわ。それには鉤爪や牙があるわけでもない。私には聞こえる…彼らにはリーダーがいるわ。そして、彼はあなたが思うより近くにいる…」
languages.original_text: "There are worse beasts lurking in this jungle, and they don't have claws and fangs. I can hear... they have a leader among them. And he is closer than you think..."

languages.text: "In diesem Urwald lauern weit schlimmere Bestien ... und sie haben kleine Klauen und Zähne. Ich kann hören ... dass unter ihnen ein Anführer ist. Und er ist näher, als Ihr denkt ..."
languages.original_text: "There are worse beasts lurking in this jungle, and they don't have claws and fangs. I can hear... they have a leader among them. And he is closer than you think..."

languages.text: « Des créatures bien pires rôdent dans cette jungle. Des créatures sans crocs ni griffes. Je les entends... Elles ont un chef. Et il est plus proche que vous le croyez... »

languages.text: "Bu ormanda kol gezen daha beter yaratıklar da var. Pençeleri veya dişleri olmayan yaratıklar... Duyabiliyorum... Bir liderleri var ve sana sandığından daha da yakın."
